Package game

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GameMode
    A game mode is a strategy a Game can follow.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CTFMode
    In CTFMode the goal for each player is to capture the flag of the other players.
    Game
    A class representing a game.
    GameRunner
    The class that start the GUI and offers methods to start new games.
    RaceMode
    In RaceMode the goal for each player is to reach the starting location of the other player or to enclose the other player such that he cannot make a move.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GameEvent
    An event sent by the Game when notifying its observers.
